entries.title_d: The Imperial space station commander is trying to escape! Eliminate him before he can jump to lightspeed!
entries.title: Endor system: Prevent the station commander from escaping.
entries.quest_target_d: The station commander is travelling in a heavily armored and armed shuttle model 'Lambda'. He's also got a large escort so prepare for a difficult battle.
entries.quest_location_d: Most of the Imperial forces are either fleeing or trying to get reinforcements. The area still have a lot of them though so stay on your toes!
entries.failed_escape: Bah, he got away! This will go in to your record pilot. Return to base.
entries.escort_wiped_out: General Ufwol: < His escort is terminated, now take that shuttle down! >
entries.escort_remaining: General Ufwol: < Concentrate on the commander pilot, you can't let him get away. >
entries.assassinate_success: Excellent pilot, looks like I sent the right man for the job. Return to base.
entries.arrival_phase_2: This is the last known location of the commander, intercept and destroy his shuttle!
entries.arrival_phase_1: Several of the station officers are trying to escape. We're sending you after the commander, don't disappoint me pilot.
